{"tid":795092,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返一份自己無興趣既工真係好痛苦","createTime":"2018-08-26T17:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T15:37:34.000Z","uid":27251,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"78cf6f5228beb5655abf783c05fa646c8f28f34f","tid":795092,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"一早起身，又磨時間又無野學...<br />\n望住幾個後生過我幾年，同一個位做左四五年，晚晚OT為左份糧大少少，日日做十幾個鐘，有時都好想唔禮貌咁問佢地，到底你地會唔會有一刻諗緊，自己廿幾歲返份咁既工做咩。<br />\n<br />\n我剛剛過左兩個半月就頂唔順了，明天辭職，要等一個月通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ed9348ab62c5478f7cc7770afef36fa78f0d89","tid":795092,"uid":20163,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"有乜工你有興趣"},{"pid":"6a82afafec7de43c86baee70508a4506d554bec2","tid":795092,"uid":88999,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"將興趣變成工作會壓力好大<br />\n你以為工作於娛樂<br />\n實際係你連娛樂都變埋工作"},{"pid":"a26eed964ff25a412f2c126179e21e0d20076d51","tid":795092,"uid":176061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"我本身對個樣野好有興趣<br />\n但變做事業後<br />\n唔想再掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12217af52ed0e57184fb5781e7d79f41eecfe6d","tid":795092,"uid":142252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:10:55.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做緊嘅野同當初in嘅唔同，一個人做幾個人嘅野。老細重要覺得成效唔大，呢排比埋啲on9 tasks<br />\n但因為fg要經驗,要等多3個月先辭得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3個月好難捱"},{"pid":"fa98e65a7d7ce10cb4e6a94e18cda86e569bb318","tid":795092,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7ed9348ab62c5478f7cc7770afef36fa78f0d89","tid":795092,"uid":20163,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"有乜工你有興趣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"準備讀UX課程"},{"